+SkinThickness: dy np gp da (mm).

+Insulin: Nng insulin huyt thanh (mu U/ml).

+BMI: Ch s khi c th (kg/m).

+DiabetesPedigreeFunction: Ch s di truyn lin quan n nguy c i tho ng.

+Age: Tui bnh nhn.

+Outcome: Nhn u ra (1 = mc bnh i tho ng, 0 = khng mc).

-Kt qu mong i:

+Xy dng m hnh phn loi d on gi tr Outcome (mc bnh hoc khng).

+nh gi m hnh bng cc ch s nh Accuracy, Precision, Recall, F1-score.

(4) Mi tng quan gia cc tnh cht (Correlations)

S tng quan (correlation) cp n mi quan h gia hai bin v cch chng c th c hoc khng cng nhau thay i.

Phng php ph bin nht tnh ton tng quan l Pearson's Correlation Coeficient, gi nh c mt phn phi chun ca cc thuc tnh lin quan. Tng quan -1 hoc 1 cho thy mi tng quan m hoc dng y tng ng. Trong khi gi tr 0 hin th khng tng quan tt c.

$$ r = \frac{\sum_{i=1}^{n} (x_i - \bar{x})(y_i - \bar{y})} {\sqrt{\sum_{i=1}^{n} (x_i - \bar{x})^2 \; \sum_{i=1}^{n} (y_i - \bar{y})^2}} $$

Mt s thut ton hc my nh hi quy tuyn tnh v logistic c hiu sut km nu c cc thuc tnh tng quan cao trong tp d liu ca bn.

Nh vy, tht s cn thit xem xt tt c cc mi tng quan theo cp ca cc thuc tnh trong tp d liu.

# 1. Chuyn tt c ct sang kiu s
cols = ['Pregnancies','Glucose','BloodPressure','SkinThickness',
        'Insulin','BMI','DiabetesPedigreeFunction','Age','Outcome']
df_dataset[cols] = df_dataset[cols].apply(pd.to_numeric, errors='coerce')

# 2. Thay th gi tr 0 bng NaN cho nhng ct khng hp l khi c 0
cols_with_zero_invalid = ['Glucose','BloodPressure','SkinThickness','Insulin','BMI']
df_dataset[cols_with_zero_invalid] = df_dataset[cols_with_zero_invalid].replace(0, np.nan)

# 3. Loi b gi tr bt thng trong Outcome
df_dataset = df_dataset[df_dataset['Outcome'].isin([0,1])]

# 4. in gi tr thiu bng median
for col in cols_with_zero_invalid:
    df_dataset[col].fillna(df_dataset[col].median(), inplace=True)

# 5. Chun ha d liu (Z-score)
scaler = StandardScaler()
df_scaled = df_dataset.copy()
df_scaled[cols[:-1]] = scaler.fit_transform(df_scaled[cols[:-1]])

print(df_scaled.head())

3.2. Hin th d liu (Visualize Data)

(1) Hin th trn tng tnh cht n (Univariate Plots)

So snh cc trung v (median) tng ng ca mi hp (box plot). Nu ng trung v ca mt hp nm bn ngoi ca mt hp so snh, th c th c s khc bit gia hai nhm.

So snh chiu di hp kim tra cch d liu c phn tn gia mi mu. Hp cng di th d liu cng phn tn. D liu cng nh cng t b phn tn.

Mt ngoi l (outlier) c nh ngha l mt im d liu nm bn ngoi phn ra (whiskers) ca hp. Kim tra hng lch ca d liu (cn i, cc phn t tp trung tri, phi).

Median gia hp v ru (whiskers) hai bn nh nhau th phn b l i xng.

Median gn y hp hn v nu ru ngn hn u di ca hp, th phn phi l lch dng (lch phi).

Median gn u hp hn v nu ru ngn hn u trn ca hp, th phn b b lch m (lch tri).

(4) Chun ha d liu (Data Normalize)

Chun ha cc tnh cht a v cng mt min tr

Min-Max Normalization

$$ z = \frac{x - \min(x)}{\max(x) - \min(x)} $$

Standard Normalization (Z-score)

$$ z = \frac{x - \mu}{\sigma} $$

Lu : Qu trnh chun ha c th lm trong phn thc nghim thut ton
